name: 费拉特·阿尔图梅瑟
name_full: 费拉特·阿尔图梅瑟 Firat Altunmese
introduction: He is Turkish actor who son of singer Izzet Altinmese. He is best known for romantic comedy "Kacak Gelinler" alongside Furkan Andic, Selin Sekerci, Deniz Baysal, Acelya Topaloglu Firat Albayram.He played in awarded film "Sofra Sirlari" alongside Demet Evgar and youth film Hesapta Ask".
